      "example": "<!-- Appliqué automatiquement via signature.css sur tous les .section-header .overline -->\n<div class=\"section-header\">\n  <span class=\"overline\">Catégorie</span>\n  <h2>Titre section</h2>\n</div>"
    },
    {
      "name": "texture-grain",
      "page": "fondation",
      "cssClasses": [],
      "jsInit": null,
      "description": "Token texture grain (v2.42.0). --texture-grain (URL SVG feTurbulence inline) + --texture-grain-opacity (0.015). Appliqué via body::after en fixed inset:0 z-index:9999 pointer-events:none. Absorbe ticket #12 (--noise-texture formalisé). Documenté dans fondation.html#texture.",
      "example": "/* tokens.css */\n--texture-grain: url(\"data:image/svg+xml,...\");\n--texture-grain-opacity: 0.015;\n\n/* styles.css */\nbody::after {\n  background-image: var(--texture-grain);\n  opacity: var(--texture-grain-opacity);\n}"
    },
    {
